{"tid":1060201,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Windows 7 應該也收到 Microsoft 的通知：這個版本將終止支援","createTime":"2019-03-13T15:20:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-13T17:14:19.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"64024fbece1dcb038759c3279713b189ed9f48c5","tid":1060201,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T15:20:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.techapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/surface-windows-7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.techapple.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2Fsurface-windows-7.jpg&h=bac62c72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nMicrosoft計劃通知Windows 7的用戶其軟件將於2020年1月14日停止更新，並在下個月開始向消費者發出關於這個截止日期的警告。這個終止日期意味著Windows 7和Office 2010將不再接收安全更新，該公司希望用家升級到Windows 10 PC和Office 365。 然而，該通知不會特別提及升級到Windows 10，但它會加入鏈接: <a href=\"http://microsoft.com/windows7，這個網站將鼓勵消費者升級到Windows\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmicrosoft.com%2Fwindows7%EF%BC%8C%E9%80%99%E5%80%8B%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99%E5%B0%87%E9%BC%93%E5%8B%B5%E6%B6%88%E8%B2%BB%E8%80%85%E5%8D%87%E7%B4%9A%E5%88%B0Windows&d=ctOUxKLv%2B9zBCrzB%2FMEnrQbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=6fc86221\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">microsoft.com/windows7，這個網站將鼓勵消費者升級到Windows</a> 10或購買更新的PC。 <br />\n<br />\nMicrosoft 從免費Windows 10升級的通知中可以看到，Windows 7用戶可以在通知上選擇&ldquo;不再提醒我&rdquo;，這樣用家就看不到通知。如果他們只是關閉提示來解除它，那麼通知在稍後的時間都會再次出現。微軟表示，它只會在2019年顯示「少數幾次」，一旦Windows 7支持在1月結束，通知將停止。Microsoft 是次並沒有透露通知的外觀和內容，直至它準備好在下個月開始將這些通知推送到用家上，因此它可以確保惡意攻擊者不會嘗試複製它並欺騙Windows 7的用戶。<br />\n<br />\nWindows 10 的市場份額在較早時超越了Windows 7，大概超過8億台設備上正在使用Windows 10，接近Microsoft 早前訂弄10億台的目標。預計是次Windows 7升級週期可以幫助Microsoft 達到此目標。"},{"pid":"91bc1b8fd256a54ab9fe5812d900d4efe7bb2d02","tid":1060201,"uid":48362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T15:22:31.000Z","msg":"M$ <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"665bc0daafa5f3c5a2e3a66005e5b8c5d4117cf6","tid":1060201,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T15:22:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.techapple.com/archives/29299\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.techapple.com%2Farchives%2F29299&d=ctOUxKLv%2B9zBCrzB%2FMEnrQbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=fbd6f6d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.techapple.com/archives/29299</a>"},{"pid":"62bcf26e0b8016a4527f68acae594aaa7bed0462","tid":1060201,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T17:07:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7d17be3130cdf833f8ac8cd749bc87bdb594750","tid":1060201,"uid":122570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T17:09:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cacd2419f8d58e0f6154f85d7881b3a7d3f8eaa","tid":1060201,"uid":59976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T17:14:19.000Z","msg":"另一邊箱, ms又將directx 12下放win7幫佢續命<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://blogs.msdn.microsoft.com/directx/2019/03/12/world-of-warcraft-uses-directx-12-running-on-windows-7/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblogs.msdn.microsoft.com%2Fdirectx%2F2019%2F03%2F12%2Fworld-of-warcraft-uses-directx-12-running-on-windows-7%2F&d=ctOUxKLv%2B9zBCrzB%2FMEnrQbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=cf50663b\" target=\"_blank\">https://blogs.msdn.microsoft.com/directx/2019/03/12/world-of-warcraft-uses-directx-12-running-on-windows-7/</a>"}]}